  npc: 0
  sequence:
  - dialogueText: You look more... prepared. I assume your meeting with the Indian
      was productive?
    buttonText: Got the hardware
  - dialogueText: I get it. It's a significant asset to have, even if it carries
      its own set of complications.
    buttonText: Keep it quiet
  - dialogueText: We should avoid attracting attention. Still, it could be useful
      later. Better to be ready for anything.
    buttonText: I know
